### SIRHA API - Casos de Prueba de Observaciones
### Pruebas para FEAT-018 US-0070: Persistir Observaciones

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000
@contentType = application/json

### ===========================================
### 1. OBSERVACIONES VÁLIDAS
### ===========================================

### 1.1 Observaciones normales (Debe retornar 200)
POST {{baseUrl}}/observations-examples/student
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "EST001",
  "firstName": "Juan",
  "lastName": "Pérez",
  "programId": "60d5ecb8b0a7c4b4b8b9b1a1",
  "observations": "Estudiante destacado en matemáticas.\nRequiere apoyo en inglés."
}

### 1.2 Observaciones con saltos de línea múltiples (Se normalizan)
POST {{baseUrl}}/observations-examples/student
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "EST002",
  "firstName": "María",
  "lastName": "García",
  "programId": "60d5ecb8b0a7c4b4b8b9b1a1",
  "observations": "Estudiante excelente.\n\n\n\nMuy responsable.\n\n\n\nSiempre puntual."
}

### ===========================================
### 2. SANITIZACIÓN DE CONTENIDO PELIGROSO
### ===========================================

### 2.1 HTML y scripts peligrosos (Se sanitiza)
POST {{baseUrl}}/observations-examples/student
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "EST003",
  "firstName": "Carlos",
  "lastName": "López",
  "programId": "60d5ecb8b0a7c4b4b8b9b1a1",
  "observations": "<script>alert('hack')</script>Estudiante <b>excelente</b>.\n<img src='x' onerror='alert(1)'>Muy responsable."
}

### 2.2 Inyección de código malicioso (Se sanitiza)
POST {{baseUrl}}/observations-examples/student
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "EST004",
  "firstName": "Ana",
  "lastName": "Martínez",
  "programId": "60d5ecb8b0a7c4b4b8b9b1a1",
  "observations": "<iframe src='javascript:alert(1)'></iframe>\n<a href='javascript:void(0)' onclick='alert(1)'>Click</a>\nEstudiante normal."
}

### 2.3 Tags HTML diversos (Se remueven)
POST {{baseUrl}}/observations-examples/student
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "EST005",
  "firstName": "Luis",
  "lastName": "Rodríguez",
  "programId": "60d5ecb8b0a7c4b4b8b9b1a1",
  "observations": "<div><p>Estudiante <strong>destacado</strong></p><ul><li>Matemáticas</li><li>Física</li></ul></div>"
}

